  },
  {
    icon: '⚡',
    title: 'Captures Annual Service Opportunities',
    text: "Facilities managers browse your commercial CCTV and alarm installations on Facebook and message — 'want to switch our annual maintenance to your firm, currently NSI Gold, sixteen cameras and Texecom alarm.' The AI captures the system details and the contract status."
  },
  {
